==Tailoring==
Yam can be used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] to create the dyeable [[Tailoring|Button Down Shirt]].  [[File:Shirt140.png|24px]] It can be used in [[dyeing]], serving as an orange dye at the dye pots, located in [[Emily]]'s and [[Haley]]'s house, [[2 Willow Lane]].

==Quests==
*Yam may be randomly requested in [[Fall]] at the [[Quests#Help Wanted Quests|"Help Wanted" board]] outside [[Pierre's General Store]] for a reward of {{Price|480}} and 150 [[Friendship]] points.

==History==
{{History|1.4|Can now be used in [[Tailoring]].}}
{{History|1.5|Iridium quality is now possible when using [[Deluxe Fertilizer]].  Bugfix for stages of growth with [[Deluxe Speed-Gro]] + [[Skills#Farming|Agriculturist]].}}

